Title: IMPACT! Wrestling - February 23, 2023

Title: IMPACT! Wrestling - February 2, 2023
description: IMPACT! returns to Orlando, Florida with a loaded show, as IMPACT World Champion Josh Alexander joins forces with No. 1 contender Rich Swann, Frankie Kazarian & Yuya Uemara to battle the team of The Design & Sami Callihan in an 8 Man tag team main event. The Bullet Club pairing of Chris Bey & Ace Austin takes on the team of Kevin Knight & Kushida. Newcomer Sheldon Jean looks to right his ship after coming up short in his IMPACT Wrestling debut last week, as he goes one-on-one with Decay’s Crazzy Steve. Plus Gisele Shaw battles Savannah Evans in Knockouts action.
